        "Description": "In an alternate universe, Agent 47 was dispatched to solve a murder. It is not believed the murderer knew that Alexa Carisle was still alive and faked her own death to hide from the enemies of the agency.  Madam Carisle is at the estate but she does not know that Agent 47 is on the way to help her.  Agent 47 has full authorization to eliminate the threat. This is also an opportunity to make an ally out of Alexa and gain access to secret files on agency traitors.",
